
    Opedbox shutdown dialog

    - GTK/Cairo based shutdown box styled for Openbox and others window managers

    Copyright (C) panjandrum 2011 <panjandrum@gmail.com>

    Originally based on Python code:
       oblogout by Andrew Williams <andy@tensixtyone.com>

